Subject: [PATCH] Add Deepgram Aura-2 TTS for low-confidence reprompts

Synthesizes the existing reprompt text with Deepgram Aura-2 and sends
the audio (base64 WAV) alongside the text over the reprompt message.
Falls back to text-only if synthesis fails. Test harness plays the
audio automatically.
